description: Sometimes we forget what is in our favorite dishes.  Alexa will help you remember what you need so you can cook with confidence!  No more forgetting that you need heavy whipping cream for your famous pancakes!
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask ingredient list what is in apple pie.
Alexa, ask ingredient list how to make pancakes.
Alexa, ask ingredient list what goes in scrambled eggs.
name: Recipe ingredient list
shortDescription: What is the recipe for common dishes?
